{"tid":792158,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係得我一個，打親機都對「附魔」呢回事冇乜興趣？","createTime":"2018-08-24T10:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:52:14.000Z","uid":90457,"like":12,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f6db6f5f6ac53f3a1ac2a4c3956ba1957b5cbfd8","tid":792158,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"Minecraft 完全唔會整嗰啲乜鬼嘢附魔檯，遇到任何怪都係用血同肉硬拼<br />\nSkyrim 執到啲咩「冰凍」武器都係用完就算，唔拆、理鳩佢<br />\n以前玩魔獸又係，睇見大場交易頻道啲人講「原始生命」、「原始虛空」我都唔理，唔係我唔想理，而係我冇能力理解、亦都冇必要理解，專心扑礦床，合合武器整盔甲升鍛造就算，話知附魔有幾賺錢有幾蝕錢<br />\n<br />\n同埋我嘅認知就係啲RPG驚嘅鍊金都只係整吓藥劑，我都會嘗試理解吓，但係附魔我冇本事學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003b1f0aefb9756e81c5078128092e5f9f713ab6","tid":792158,"uid":160368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"利申同你一樣感覺但個object 係藥水<br />\n咩打不死系會勁20%果d<br />\non 撚鳩又要估隻野係咩系又要特登簡番支水出黎，用又用得果幾分鐘麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc75fc86a3cf0c3e3c8ba6c4b3c1867b52e36ed","tid":792158,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"Metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎住碌棍衝上前往死裡打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1da1fefc6018bf25a5f4fda6c7ce3b3a0a0d94c","tid":792158,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"skyrim個附魔屈到我唔敢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd67a40356460ded66e907a17687f823edd4c67","tid":792158,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote